results.name: Least k for which A065413(k) = n, or 0 if no such k exists.
example: a(3) = 23 because the first occurrence of 3 in A065413 is A065413(23) = 3.
maple: # given vector A of size N constructed as in A065413
for i from 1 to N do
if B[A[i]] = 0 then B[A[i]]:= i fi
